snippet.title: In Stars and Time Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In this turn-based RPG, following an uncomfortably close encounter with a trap, party leader Siffrin discovers they are actually stuck in a time loop, able to start the day over again with nobody else the wiser.

https://www.instarsandtime.com/
